OL,3,CBus strikes to go ahead as workers
OL,4,Creject latest pay offer
OL,6,FBus strikes are set to begin across
OL,7,FWales as First Cymru workers have
OL,8,Frejected the latest pay offer from the
OL,9,Fcompany.
OL,11,FUnite the Union members voted to
OL,12,Freject the new offer tabled by First
OL,13,FCymru, which the union said had
OL,14,Fresulted in the good will suspension
OL,15,Fof strike action initially planned for
OL,16,F22nd October.
OL,18,FHowever, members have rejected the
OL,19,Foffer which they say still withheld
OL,20,Fmembers' back pay.
