OL,6,FStrike action declared for the 30th
OL,7,Fand 31st of October, and 1 and 2 of
OL,8,FNovember will now go ahead.
OL,10,FAdditional strike action declared for
OL,11,F5th, 6th, 7th and 8th November will
OL,12,Falso take place.
OL,14,FUnite say members have indicated a
OL,15,Fwillingness to escalate the dispute
OL,16,Fwith further action throughout the
OL,17,FChristmas period.
