OL,3,CBus strikes to go ahead as workers
OL,4,Creject latest pay offer
OL,6,FFirst Cymru say they have listened to
OL,7,FUnite the Union member feedback and
OL,8,Fhave tried to ensure customers who
OL,9,Frely on its services are not affected
OL,10,Fby strike action.
OL,12,FThe company says its "door remains
OL,13,Fopen to negotiation."
OL,15,FFirst Cymru predominantly serves
OL,16,FSwansea, Llanelli, Bridgend, Neath-
OL,17,FPort Talbot, Pembrokeshire and
OL,18,FCarmarthenshire, as well as routes
OL,19,Fthrough Cardiff and the Vale of
OL,20,FGlamorgan.
