OL,3,CBus strikes to go ahead as workers
OL,4,Creject latest pay offer
OL,6,FDoug Claringbold, Managing Director
OL,7,Ffor First Bus in Cymru, said: "We are
OL,8,Fdisappointed for our customers that
OL,9,Fthe above inflation pay offer we made
OL,10,Fto our colleagues, including drivers,
OL,11,Fhas been rejected and that they will
OL,12,Fnow face disruption.
OL,14,F"Throughout this extensive negotiation
OL,15,Fprocess, we have listened to Unite the
OL,16,FUnion member feedback and made a
OL,17,Fnumber of offers in order to try and
OL,18,Fsettle this dispute, to ensure
OL,19,Fcustomers who rely on our services are
OL,20,Fnot affected by strike action.
